{
  "name": "QRCoder",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "summary": "A QR code generator and scanner for OSX and iOS written in Swift.",
  "description": "Since OSX 10.9 / iOS 7 apple offers a CI filter to generate QR codes.\nHowever, scaling the QR code to the desired size without blurring\nthe image doesn't work out of the box. The QRCoder library can help you with that.\nIt also contains a handy view controller to scan QR codes.\n",
